Comment: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=====AVANT=====
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日和煦的阳光下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.03,0:00:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初夏的脚步声已渐渐传来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但仍有深陷不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是吐出冰冷的气息都要费劲全力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该怎么面对他们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.19,0:00:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样才能将温暖的音色传递给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我啊  春太
Comment: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=====A  PART=====
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫穗村千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个能华丽地吹奏长笛的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中一年级的可爱女生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从上高中才吹了一个半月的初学者而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对穗村来说还是太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音量还可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你就老老实实发传单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟嗓门大是你唯一特长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊  千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有想加入的人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有停下脚步来倾听的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来能期待一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我们从头再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是吹奏乐部的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请收下  我们是吹奏乐部的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是吹奏乐部的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  一起快乐地演奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年三班的成岛美代子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是绝对要拉进社团的人才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为双簧管吹奏者的她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初中就登上过普门馆的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她所在的仅有区区23人的小型乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首次出场就取得了银奖的惊人成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,23个人算少吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊  当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全日本吹奏乐大赛有编组上限55人的A部门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和上限30人一组的B部门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是B部门只能参加地方比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法参加在普门馆举办的全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要招多少人才能参加比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说  今年是不可能的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就目前的人数  参加B部门都悬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要听听吗  成岛同学的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我一个人住在这公寓里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我租了一间旧公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为自己的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房租和父母各付一半
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  真奢侈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我的姐姐们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南风姐  亚实姐  冬菜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里简直是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然进了单身男生的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对千夏你没兴趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是去年初中组的全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但成岛她性格有问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了掩盖你的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人数当然是越多越好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年我想参加比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在普门馆里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让草壁老师站在那里指挥一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此我们需要她的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不想再碰吹奏乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得可惜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的双簧管在哭泣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  全美国的双簧管都在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs25}注：「全美国都在哭泣」是好莱坞电影在日本经常使用的广告词\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h这里千夏误以为春太在赞美成岛的双簧管技艺精良
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千夏  你理解错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说相声的话请移步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  就当是帮我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想多费唇舌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国产全熟菠萝味到底在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千夏  钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等着  辉夜姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs25}注：辉夜姬是《竹取物语》的女主角，要求五位求婚者为她取来五样宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  成岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们不好  搅乱了你平静的校园生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往返商店街是我们自作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千夏先垫付了钱  但她丝毫没有记恨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问要多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很贵啊  毕竟是国产全熟菠萝味嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你差点买成国产全熟奇异果味了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢奇异果了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇异果是猕猴桃科猕猴桃属哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  不知道我家的猫吃不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  要多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然希望成岛同学加入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就应该更光明正大地说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就算入部了也处不来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千夏你没注意到什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射人先射马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  骗人的吧  不可能不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是心美她这么说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真华是不可能的  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是西川真由同学对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能打扰一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你来实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前和成岛同学是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我四月看到你和她一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时你就盯上成岛同学了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成岛是从别的地方搬过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初中时的朋友应该都不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从学号来看  你和她是前后座
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你主动找她搭话的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是常见的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害  上条你是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一根神棍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必你很郁闷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和成岛在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是双簧管演奏者的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双簧管的音色会受演奏者的个性影响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一种非常纤细的乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果长期演奏  性格会变得沉闷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这也是成岛同学全身心投入双簧管演奏的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想要成为她的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是美代子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道她放弃双簧管的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去年在全国大会现场听过她的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部曲目结束之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听见了一声尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后的颁奖典礼上没有看到她的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这件事有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天  美代子的弟弟去世了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=====B  PART=====
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的弟弟长期住院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天病情突然恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母当时也身在会场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一人陪在他的身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才埋怨自己  放弃双簧管了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有去找她玩过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去成岛同学的家里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香  是牛肉炖汤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是西川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  欢迎  稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:09:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然打扰实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事  很久没见到美代子的朋友来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  美代子在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  叫了她但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  都是因为我们不请自来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有时间  可以慢慢等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保险  筷子我也带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千夏说她想吃牛肉炖汤…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美代子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去我房间喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉美代子  给你添麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝了就回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗  春太为了在咖啡店看完八十三卷「Patalliro!」
Comment: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs25}注：「Patalliro!」，1978年起连载的长寿BL向少女漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花了五小时才喝完一杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五分钟内喝完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要你五分钟内喝完  春太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这简直是个小博物馆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉赚到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赚到什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.23,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1c&HC4D2D2&\fs23\an3}单人跳棋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:02.57,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1c&HC4D2D2&\fs23\an6}河内塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:03.23,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1c&HE6FEFF&\fs23\an4}魔金
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:04.49,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1c&HE6FEFF&\fs23\an9}珠玑妙算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:04.99,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1c&HE6FEFF&\fs23\an8}十五数字推盘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:05.24,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1c&HE6FEFF&\fs23\an4}七巧板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:05.99,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1c&HE6FEFF&\fs23\an7}魔方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是解谜游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种古典名作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且墙上挂着的都是错觉图片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认为这些是你收集的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些书是解谜游戏爱好者的圣经
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:18.44,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(929,187)\an1\fs20\fax-0.4\frx25\frz-5\fry-30\1c&H588EAA&\bord2}解谜之王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作者杜德耐  九岁时就已显露出天才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看这情况  你平时应该不怎么翻这些书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部是你弟弟的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许他憧憬着在同世代就已经远近驰名的天才杜德耐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  他自己设计的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都签了名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对解谜游戏的这份热忱值得敬仰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论他曾身患多么严重的疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里摆放着的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弟弟曾经活在世上的宝贵证明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅只是摆设
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有好好破解它们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在的状态可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你以一己之力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担负起了种种解决不了的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说你们能解决什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是有你不能破解的谜题的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会为你分担烦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少  为这个房间里的谜题而困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再只有你一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经听过美代子全国大会时演奏的双簧管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也在会场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听的是录音磁带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小聪拜托他叔叔阿姨录下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他想守望着姐姐的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不帮他录音的话他会遗恨终身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是不幸的偶然交叠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说  谁都没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美代子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个还原试试
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔方？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一面都是白色的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在小聪留下来的解谜游戏中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这个我无论如何也解不开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个已经打乱了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打乱？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随意转动魔方的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是已经打乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还原之后是什么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小聪不肯告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我们把它还原了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能慎重考虑一下加入吹奏乐部的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期五放学之前为期限
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是个绝对无法还原的魔方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小聪留给我的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1079,565)\an5\3c&H000000&\fs30}星\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h期\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦的是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要戴手套
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不想把珍贵的遗物弄脏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗物…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1079,565)\an5\3c&H000000&\fs30}星\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h期\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发出的声音不一样之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在着微妙的色差之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(237,565)\an5\3c&H000000&\fs30}星\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h期\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h三
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是油画颜料的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:14:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在普通的魔方上面涂上了白色颜料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  成岛同学的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有谁会画油画
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千夏你一心光顾着食物了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才总是会漏掉很重要的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是我察觉到有味道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千夏  你还察觉到其他什么地方了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是多细微的事情都好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个魔方上没有小聪的签名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里都没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1079,565)\an5\3c&H000000&\fs30}星\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h期\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h四
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁早放弃  赶快去向成岛同学道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「虽然没能还原  但是还是请你加入我们部」这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天才是最后期限吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不知道还原之后是什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是没法还原的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会存在正确答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要它是谜题的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草壁老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你们说的那个魔方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样才能解开这个谜题的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不在人世了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是设计这个魔方的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经事先想到还原魔方的人出现时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己已经不在人世的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会把还原的魔方是正确的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先留在什么地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个魔方的里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要找到正确的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谜题就会顺其自然的解开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能是这么设计的吧
