Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是什么惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「con  amore」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,con  a  mo  re？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是音乐术语
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「有爱情地」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个饱含着爱意的魔方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1079,565)\an5\3c&H000000&\fs30}星\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h期\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h五
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还原了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始还原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前说过  这个魔方是留给你的惩罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小聪因为生病  从没交到朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他来说  解谜就是他的自尊心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及支撑他心灵的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他设计谜题  我来破解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我初中加入了吹奏乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只顾自己开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丢下他一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说  这个无法还原的魔方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.85,0:17:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小聪给我的遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我他是不会原谅我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个魔方确实是小聪留下来的遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始解谜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这个魔方  六个面都是白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,处于被打乱的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么转动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没法恢复成原来的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么小聪没有告诉你还原之后是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小聪希望的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能从这个被打乱的状态中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈出一步  勇于前进
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千夏  西川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  美代子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三分钟就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我  放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该向前迈出脚步了  成岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今以后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也打算以不幸为借口继续这样生活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离小聪去世才过了一年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经过了一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们的一年是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个魔方是小聪留给你的遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么  都不要踌躇不前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要勇敢的迈向前方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在纯白的世界里自己涂上颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  这就是最初的那一步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你弟弟送给你的祝福
